# List of Actors

## 1. User (Customer)

### Description
A registered user who interacts with the system to rent cars, buy cars, make payments, and manage bookings.

### Responsibilities
- Register and log in to the system
- Browse available cars for rent or sale
- Search cars using filters (location, price, type, date)
- Choose rental options (self-drive or with driver)
- Make payments using mobile banking services
- Book cars for rental
- Purchase cars for sale
- Cancel bookings and request refunds
- View booking history and payment status
- Submit customer support requests

---

## 2. Admin

### Description
System administrator responsible for managing the platform and overseeing operations.

### Responsibilities
- Manage vehicles (add, update, delete cars for rent or sale)
- Manage users (view, activate, deactivate accounts)
- Manage bookings and sales records
- Monitor payments and refunds
- Assign drivers to bookings (if driver option is selected)
- View system reports and analytics

---

## 3. Driver

### Description
A driver assigned to rental bookings when the customer selects the "with driver" option.

### Responsibilities
- View assigned trips
- Accept or reject ride assignments
- View pickup and drop-off locations using map integration

---

## 4. Customer Support

### Description
Support staff responsible for handling user issues and inquiries.

### Responsibilities
- Respond to user complaints and questions
- Assist with booking issues and cancellations
- Escalate technical or payment-related issues to admin
